      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3952 - Al-Ala narrated from Muhammad ibn Muslim who report from one of Imams (as):\nI asked Imam (as) about pledging collateral (Rahn) and having a guarantor (Kafil) in a deferred payment sale.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in it.\""
